Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:18.68,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.84,0:00:56.02,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}總有一天 向著這無望的高空
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.64,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志將一飛沖天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.91,0:01:16.72,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是戰友嗎{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.98,0:01:21.47,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}當走之路是黑暗嗎{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.07,0:01:26.96,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 在面前寒光閃動
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.11,0:01:30.84,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}無名感情在胸中翻湧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.03,0:01:36.65,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-此時此刻在此地 尚不能結束-
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.65,0:01:41.79,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}那麼就做好活下去的準備吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.91,0:01:47.04,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一腔熱忱 越積越高無處釋放
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.04,0:01:51.61,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這份量 怎可能不沉重{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.99,0:01:57.24,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}戰場之上 笑談青澀有何不可
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.24,0:02:03.87,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}我會一個一個親自去實踐
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.05,0:02:05.42,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…放馬過來{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
